class="text-sm font-bold md:text-sm">349.00 美元</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2>Final Cut Pro 2 和 Logic Pro 2 获得 AI 功能</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-3.fill.size_2000x1333.v1715093623.jpg" alt="运行 Logic Pro 2 的 iPad" width="2000" height="1333" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-3.fill.size_800x533.v1715093623.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-3.fill.size_1400x933.v1715093623.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-3.fill.size_2000x1333.v1715093623.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">信用：苹果</span></div></div><p>Apple 还推出了适用于 Final Cut Pro 和 Logic Pro 的 iPad 应用程序的新版本。这些应用程序专注于一些新的人工智能功能，这些功能利用了新 Pro 中的 M4 芯片。</p><p>苹果表示，新的 Final Cut Pro 在 M4 iPad Pro 上渲染最终输出的速度提高了两倍。新的实时多机位功能可以让您同时连接和预览最多四个摄像机，而新的应用程序 Final Cut Camera 还可以让您远程控制所有这些摄像机，包括曝光等功能。最后，您可以从外部硬盘驱动器编辑项目。</p><p> Logic Pro 2 还获得了一些新功能：“会话播放器”，它通过新的贝斯和键盘手扩展了应用程序的鼓手选项。 “ChromaGlow”可让您使用 AI 为您的曲目添加“超现实”声音。 Stem Splitter 将一个组合音轨分成不同的组件，至少分成鼓、贝斯、人声和其他乐器。</p><p> Logic Pro 2 将于 5 月 13 日作为现有用户的免费更新提供，价格仍然为每月 4.99 美元或每年 49 美元。 Final Cut Pro 2 具有相同的定价方案，但将在“今年春季晚些时候”上市。</p><h2> Apple Pencil Pro 配备了一些新传感器和触觉反馈</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-4.fill.size_2000x1007.v1715093623.jpg" alt="苹果铅笔专业版" width="2000" height="1007" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-4.fill.size_800x403.v1715093623.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-4.fill.size_1400x705.v1715093623.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-4.fill.size_2000x1007.v1715093623.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">信用：苹果</span></div></div><p>苹果最终将“Pro”放在了 Apple Pencil 上。升级后的 Apple Pencil 配备了新的传感器，可让您挤压以调出新的工具调色板。正如传闻所述，Pencil 具有用于触觉反馈的触觉引擎，因此当你挤压它时，你会感觉到轻微的振动。您还可以倾斜铅笔来实时调整铅笔笔画。</p><p> Apple Pencil 还支持“查找我的”：下次在沙发下滚动时，只需在 iPad 或 iPhone 上打开“查找我的”即可找到它。</p><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/8B24L?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Apple%20is%20charging%20%24129%20for%20the%20new%20Apple%20Pencil%20Pro&amp;short_url=8B24L&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">Apple 新款 Apple Pencil Pro 售价 129 美元</a>，将于 5 月 15 日开始发售。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">苹果铅笔专业版</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-xs font-medium md:text-xs">苹果</span><span class="text-sm font-bold md:text-sm">129.00 美元</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="py-auto flex h-full w-full flex-col justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-green text-center font-sans text-base text-white md:text-sm"><div>现在去购物</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex items-center justify-center" style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 9"><img class="max-h-full max-w-full" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-11.fill.size_autoxauto.v1715097049.jpg" alt="苹果铅笔专业版" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><img class="max-h-32 w-full" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-11.fill.size_245x245.v1715097049.jpg" alt="苹果铅笔专业版" width="245" height="245" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="py-auto flex h-full w-full flex-col justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-green text-center font-sans text-base text-white md:text-sm"><div>现在去购物</div></div></div></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-xs font-medium md:text-xs">苹果</span><span class="text-sm font-bold md:text-sm">129.00 美元</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2>妙控键盘将提供更像笔记本电脑的体验</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-5.fill.size_2000x1127.v1715093623.png" alt="新的魔术键盘" width="2000" height="1127" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-5.fill.size_800x451.v1715093623.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-5.fill.size_1400x789.v1715093623.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HX9NJFXKAR755M6B6BXAVMR7/images-5.fill.size_2000x1127.v1715093623.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">信用：苹果</span></div></div><p>为了配合新款 iPad Pro，苹果升级了妙控键盘，为用户提供更像笔记本电脑的体验。最值得注意的是，触控板变得更大了，现在有一整排功能键，掌托现在由铝制成。</p><p>苹果的网站没有提及具体的触控板尺寸，但它确实证实了新的触控板将全程提供完整的触觉反馈，有助于它与 MacBook 保持同等水平。不幸的是，新的妙控键盘无法与新的 iPad Air 型号配合使用，这意味着只有 Pro 用户才能使用铝制掌托和新的 14 键功能排。</p><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/eB6PJ?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=11-inch%20Magic%20Keyboard%20will%20run%20you%20%24299&amp;short_url=eB6PJ&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">11 英寸妙控键盘售价为 299 美元</a>， <a href="https://zdcs.link/PyR7V?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=the%2013-inch%20one%20costs%20%24349&amp;short_url=PyR7V&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">13 英寸妙控键盘售价为 349 美元</a>。它有两种颜色可供选择：黑色和传统的苹果灰。您今天就可以订购，并将于 5 月 15 日开始供货。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">适用于 iPad Pro 的妙控键盘（11 英寸）</div><div class="mt-4 block font-sans text-sm font-medium leading-5 text-gray-900 md:mx-0 md:mt-2">也适用于 13 英寸 iPad Pro。 </div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-xs font-medium md:text-xs">苹果</span><span class="text-sm font-bold md:text-sm">299.00 美元</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="py-auto flex h-full w-full flex-col justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-green text-center font-sans text-base text-white md:text-sm"><div>现在去购物</di